General.Name: Euroafrica Digital Ventures AB
General.Description: Euroafrica Digital Ventures AB (publ) owns and operates services and platforms for B2B and B2C markets. It develops Software as a Service platforms that offer media planning, campaign optimization, publishing, and results follow up; and Kupatana, a buying and selling site in Tanzania. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden. Euroafrica Digital Ventures AB (publ) operates as a subsidiary of Skandnet Group AB.
